## SSH Access

You have SSH keys mounted at `/home/node/.ssh/`. Access cluster nodes via:

```bash
# Control plane
ssh kube501    # 192.168.1.51
ssh kube502    # 192.168.1.52
ssh kube503    # 192.168.1.53

# Worker
ssh kube511    # 192.168.1.61

# Proxmox host (for VM management)
ssh node005    # 192.168.1.105
```

kubectl config should be available via SSH to any control plane node:
```bash
ssh kube501 'kubectl get nodes'
ssh kube501 'kubectl get pods --all-namespaces'
```

